General introduction:
--------------------
openBibleViewer is a bible study application based on C++11, Qt >= 4.6 and CLucene >= 2.3.3.4.

If you found a bug, please report it on <https://github.com/metaxy/openBibleViewer/issues>.

Read the file INSTALL how to install and compile this version of openBibleViewer. There's also a SPEC file
to create RPMs, it's called openBibleViewer.spec.

Requirements:
-------------
See file INSTALL for detailed installation instructions.

Documentation:
--------------
You can find information about openBibleViewer, the installation and usage on the website: <http://metaxy.github.io/openBibleViewer/>


Paul Walger
